# Frontend Architecture

- Use React + TypeScript + Vite project conventions.
- Keep components small, focused, and reusable.
- Put API clients and HTTP logic in `src/services/`.
- Put shared domain and transport types in `src/types/`.
- Put response parsing and normalization in `src/utils/`.
- Keep rendering and side effects separate; do not mix UI markup with API call logic.
